                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.105/37: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-10-18T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 18, 1923—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>224. Your No. 346 October 14, 2 p.m.<note n="24" xml:id="d563fn24">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_520">p. 520</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p>Please report by telegraph concerning the oral understanding between the Dean and
                    the Ministry of Foreign Affairs relating to the railway police scheme.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
